      "writtenOn": "2016-05-19T16:18:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "shouldn\u0027t that the OK state. \n\nJust making sure we are on the same page here:\n\ndeterministic alarms have two states OK and ALARM\n\nnon-deterministic alarms have three states UNDETERMINED, OK and ALARM",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 490,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 490,
        "endChar": 13
      },
